@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="display-4 text-success">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
        <p class="lead text-muted">Your trust is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you make a donation or interact with our services.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-5">
        <h3 class="text-primary">1. Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>When you donate, we may collect the following information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Personal Information</strong> - such as your name, email address, phone number, and GCash number (if provided).</li>
            <li><strong>Payment Information</strong> - details related to the donation, including the amount donated and payment method.</li>
            <li><strong>Transaction History</strong> - records of your donations and related communications.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4">
        <h3 class="text-primary">2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <p>We use the information we collect in the following ways:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>To Process Donations</strong> - We use your information to process and acknowledge your donation securely.</li>
            <li><strong>To Communicate</strong> - We may send you confirmation emails, receipts, and updates about our charity's activities.</li>
            <li><strong>To Improve Our Services</strong> - Your data helps us understand our donors and improve our donation process.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4">
        <h3 class="text-primary">3. Data Protection</h3>
        <p>Your personal data is important to us, and we are committed to protecting it. We use industry-standard encryption techniques to ensure your donation and personal information are safe and secure.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4">
        <h3 class="text-primary">4. Sharing Your Information</h3>
        <p>We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties. However, we may need to share your information with trusted partners such as payment processors, only as necessary to process your donation securely.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4">
        <h3 class="text-primary">5. Your Rights</h3>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Access Your Data</strong> - You may request information about the data we hold about you.</li>
            <li><strong>Correct Your Information</strong> - You can update or correct your personal details.</li>
            <li><strong>Delete Your Information</strong> - You may request the removal of your data from our system, except for records required for legal or regulatory purposes.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4">
        <h3 class="text-primary">6. Contact Us</h3>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns regarding your privacy or this policy, please contact us at:</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> heartfund3@gmail.com</p>
        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (049) 5626-296</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-5">
        <p class="text-muted text-center">Last Updated: December 2024</p>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Optional Custom CSS for more styling -->
<style>
    body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }

    .container {
        background-color: #f7f7f7;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h1 {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #28a745; /* Green color for titles */
    }

    h3 {
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #007bff; /* Blue for section titles */
    }

    ul {
        padding-left: 20px;
        list-style-type: disc;
    }

    p {
        font-weight: 400;
    }

    .text-muted {
        color: #6c757d;
    }

    .mt-4, .mt-5 {
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .text-center {
        text-align: center;
    }
</style>
